data.description: Welcome to your secluded retreat in the heart of nature! This charming ranch-style home nestled on five private acres offers the perfect blend of comfort and tranquility. Surrounded by lush woodlands and abundant wildlife, this property is a nature lover's dream. A meandering stream adds to the serene ambiance, making it your very own oasis. Step inside this cozy home and find a open floor plan that's perfect for relaxation. The kitchen has updated appliances, hardwood floors in the kitchen and living room. The primary bedroom boasts a primary bathroom for added convenience,. The partially finished basement has a room that can also be used as a bedroom (NTC) and a rough in for another bathroom. And there is a large wood stove that will keep you warm all winter. The exterior of this property is a true paradise. Enjoy the serenity of your wooded surroundings, explore the wildlife, enjoy the evenings around the fire or playing horseshoes with family and friends.  With two sheds and a detached covered carport, you'll have ample space for outdoor equipment, hobbies, and parking. Don't miss this rare opportunity to own a secluded retreat with endless possibilities. Whether you're seeking a peaceful escape from the hustle and bustle or a place to call home, this property offers it all. Schedule your private tour today and experience the beauty of country living at its finest!
